{
  "stem": "5891.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, you don't last but six, eight months, you're finished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sooner or later, you're going to get it, no matter how quarantined you are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's in the air.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're exposed to all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we don't have any special privileges.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got to wash block, just like them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a wash thing where we washed our little thingies out with, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have any, just to keep half decently clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But how much can you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't have any soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't got nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't do much there, OK?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only more.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What job did you have after you were not working in the kitchen because of the typhus?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went out to the aussenkommando.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You get up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You stand in line.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You pick up that bowl of soup or bowl of tea, whatever they called it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you got your [GERMAN], your quarter of a loaf, that thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you line up, and you're marching out to the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we have done anything from building roads, building railroad tracks, fields, in the rain, in the snow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got scars all over my feet, yet, from the wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got all kinds of scars on my feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Wrapped the rags around it and all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, on the aussenkommando, most of the time-- and we were on the aussenkommando outside-- we had woman guards.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think woman guards, woman and woman is a terrible, terrible situation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There is no feeling between woman, when a woman is an authority over you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, what did they do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Old ladies-- I remember, there was a woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was 64 years old, happened to be a German woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was on my block.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
